Assuming Ubuntu...

Install MongoDB
Install any MongoDB Manager. I used robomongo

Create a database name grep
Add a collection named users
Add the following document in it: 
	{
	    "username" : "tanmay",
	    "email" : "someEmail",
	    "password" : "password",
	    "role" : "ADMIN"
	}

Install node
	"npm install" in the grep folder... ignore the linting errors for now. Have just added the linter. Will fix the errors soon.

"node server.js" to start the server 
